snippet.title: Project: Nightlight - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming in Q1 2023. Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2200330/Project_Nightlight/

Project: Nightlight is an atmospheric VR horror game where, as a security guard, it is your job to protect the facility. At the mercy of the radio’s instruction, you are urged deeper into the building to ensure the safety of The Artifact.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/FringeRealities
Discord: https://discord.gg/AqVtfyQ5
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@fringerealites
